OL,3,CTwo arrests and 'stolen' caravans
OL,4,Crecovered in crackdown ahead of
OL,5,CAppleby Fair
OL,7,FTwo men have been arrested as part of
OL,8,Fa crackdown on stolen vehicles being
OL,9,Fbrought into Cumbria ahead of the
OL,10,FAppleby Horse Fair.
OL,12,FCumbria Police found a pick-up truck
OL,13,Fand four caravans in the county, which
OL,14,Fthey believe have been stolen.
OL,16,FOfficers first recovered a Toyota
OL,17,FHilux pick-up truck in the Brough area
OL,18,Fwhich they suspected was stolen from
OL,19,Fthe Essex area.
