OL,7,FA 27-year-old man from the Kent area
OL,8,Fwas arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fpossession of a stolen vehicle and
OL,10,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
OL,12,FHe has since been released on police
OL,13,Fbail with conditions not to re-enter
OL,14,FCumbria.
OL,16,FOfficers then attended Powis Lane in
OL,17,Fthe Long Marton area, where they
OL,18,Frecovered four caravans, suspected to
OL,19,Fbe stolen.
