OL,4,Crecovered in crackdown ahead of
OL,5,CAppleby Fair
OL,7,FThree of the caravans are believed to
OL,8,Fbelong to owners in the south of
OL,9,FEngland, whilst the fourth is believed
OL,10,Fto belong to someone in Wales.
OL,12,FOfficers have said they are working to
OL,13,Fcontact the owners.
OL,15,FA 38-year-old man, also from the Kent
OL,16,Farea, was arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Ftheft of a motor vehicle.
