OL,3,CTwo arrests and 'stolen' caravans
OL,4,Crecovered in crackdown ahead of
OL,5,CAppleby Fair
OL,7,FSuperintendent Dan St Quintin, Gold
OL,8,FCommander for Appleby Horse Fair,
OL,9,Fsaid: "As we head towards the 2024
OL,10,FAppleby Horse Fair, officers are
OL,11,Fworking to identify and take
OL,12,Fenforcement action against the
OL,13,Fminority who either come to the county
OL,14,Fintent on committing offences or come
OL,15,Fhere after committing offences
OL,16,Felsewhere.
OL,18,F"This will enable the vast majority of
OL,19,Fpeople coming to the Fair who are law-
OL,20,Fabiding to enjoy it.
