OL,3,CTwo arrests and 'stolen' caravans
OL,4,Crecovered in crackdown ahead of
OL,5,CAppleby Fair
OL,7,F"The enforcement action taken
OL,8,Fyesterday was significant but will by
OL,9,Fno means be the last. Where there is
OL,10,Fevidence of criminality, officers will
OL,11,Fbe swift in making arrests and
OL,12,Frecovering property."
OL,14,FThe operation continued to the South
OL,15,FLakes area on Saturday (25 May 2024),
OL,16,Fwhere officers discovered an
OL,17,Funauthorised encampment at a field in
OL,18,FKirkby Lonsdale.
