OL,7,FThose on the field were given a
OL,8,Fdirection to leave and moved on under
OL,9,FSection 61 of the Criminal Justice and
OL,10,FPublic Order Act 1994 powers.
OL,12,FA total of 13 caravans and vehicles
OL,13,Fwere moved on as a result of the
OL,14,Faction taken.
